                    <div id="about-modal" class="modal">
                        <h1>PStreamer</h1>
                        <p>PStreamer is a peer to peer screen sharing project. It aims to provide low latency and secure 
                            streaming without any server needed for transmission. Because everything is peer to peer, streaming a source to
                            two people instead of one uses twice as much bandwith, so be cautious. You can change the quality in the settings to
                            reduce the bitrate. PStreamer uses a technology called WebRTC which is used for video transmission. Happy streaming!</p>
